summary: There are some YouTube channels that just are meant to be binged watched rather than watching each new video as it comes out,...
body:
There are some YouTube channels that just are meant to be binged watched rather than watching each new video as it comes out, the creators don’t intend that but that’s just how it is

ex: buzzfeed, game theory, the try guys, cinemasins

they’re just far more satisfying to watch 4 hours worth of content in a row than watch one video regularly

summary: hi, im the girl who asked one of the last question, and i was wondering if you could list some bi and lesbian youtubers?
question: hi, im the girl who asked one of the last question, and i was wondering if you could list some bi and lesbian youtubers?
answer:
Yeah, no problem! 💕 they’re ranked kinda in the amount I generally watch them, and of course we probably have different taste in youtubers so I tried to give some variety. Hope you find one you like!

  • Jessie Paege (bi & aspec)
  • Keara Graves (bi/queer, plus her sapphic queer non-binary (ex?)partner, Sarah Webber!)
  • Alayna Joy (bisexual/queer)
  • Rowen Ellis (lesbian & aspec)
  • Marinashutup (bisexual, but only watch her if you enjoy feminist videos!)
  • thenotadam (a bisexual guy, but he’s got some pretty good videos on bisexuality!)
  • Jessica Kellgren-Fozard (lesbian, plus you get to see her wife too!)
  • Katzun (bi, prefers girls)
  • Dodie/doddlevloggle (bisexual)
  • ElleOfTheMills (bisexual)
  • Georgia Bridgers (bisexual)
  • Rebecca Shoptaw (she makes queer short movies!!)
  • nowthisisliving (lesbian)
  • Stevie (lesbian)
  • Ally Hills (lesbian)
  • Cammie Scott (lesbian)
  • Marie Jacquemin (lesbian)
  • Tanya Zhang (lesbian)

Queer musical youtubers!

  • Chloe Moriondo
  • Abbey Glover
  • girl in red
  • Hayley Kiyoko (lesbian)
  • Dodie (bisexual)
